KBC Hired Goldman, Merrill to ‘Check Asset Values,’ Polish Unit’s CEO Says

-- B y   P a w e l   K o z l o w s k i
-- 
2011-06-30T08:08:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/kbc-hired-goldman-merrill-to-check-asset-values-bardan-says.html
KBC Groep NV (KBC)  has hired Goldman Sachs
Group Inc. and Merrill Lynch to help it “check the value of
assets” as the Belgian financial-services group needs to repay
state aid, Maciej Bardan, chief executive officer of  Poland ’s
 Kredyt Bank SA (KRB) , said in an interview with TVN CNBC today.  Bardan declined to say if KBC plans to sell its majority
stake in Warsaw-based Kredyt Bank.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Pawel Kozlowski at 
 pkozlowski@bloomberg.net  